title: Cool New Android Apps - Febuary 2017 [Ep#8]
description:
So, here is another episode of cool new apps for Feb 2017.  These may not be must have Android apps or best Android apps, but all of these apps are new and do something, that has never been done before. 

Apps Used in this video

1. Touch Circle https://goo.gl/8tUi7L
2. YouTube Go - https://goo.gl/rgAfot
3. Keyusic - https://goo.gl/tEu3fl
4. Yalp Store - https://goo.gl/GCXcg8
5. Volume slider - https://goo.gl/uJfusg
6. Smart Drawer - https://goo.gl/k8Xt4z


Other Apps you should check out

WiFi reminder - reminds you when you connect or disconnect a wireless device (https://goo.gl/REwIhr)
InstaSave -  adds a download button to all Instagram photos and Videos (https://goo.gl/BBujLJ)
Cornerfly - adds rounded corners to your display (https://goo.gl/k0SyFJ)
